properties.headline: Gale Warning issued February 20 at 1:51PM CST until February 22 at 12:00AM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
...GUSTY WINDS AND HIGH WAVES FRIDAY INTO FRIDAY NIGHT...

* WHAT...Southwest winds 25 to 35 kt with gusts up to 40 kt and
waves 8 to 14 feet expected.

* WHERE...Open waters over the north half of Lake Michigan.

* WHEN...From 9 AM Friday to midnight CST Friday night.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM FRIDAY TO MIDNIGHT CST FRIDAY NIGHT
